cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper involves computer vision (CV) and natural language processing (NLP) tasks, specifically image captioning. Therefore, cs.CV and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes a method that involves learning a mapping function, which falls under machine learning (LG) and artificial intelligence (AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper evaluates its method on image datasets, which falls under multimedia (MM) sub-category.
